  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>How to send a fax</title>
  </head>
  <body alink="#EE0000" bgcolor="#cccccc" link="#0000EE" text="#000000"
    vlink="#551A8B">
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <div align="center"> <big><big><big><b>Sending a fax:</b></big></big></big></div>
    <ol>
      <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-position:
        inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><br>
      </li>
      <big> </big>
    </ol>
    <table border="5" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2" width="100%">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td valign="top"><big><big>
            <%= image_tag "help/machine.PNG" %>
          </big></big></td>
          <td bgcolor="#99ffff" valign="top">
            <ol>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big>Make
                  sure the fax machine is plugged into a power source
                  and also plugged into a working phone jack.</big></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big><big>Turn
                    the fax machine on.</big></big></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big><big>Obtain
                    the fax number of the des<b>tination fax machine.</b></big></big></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big><b><big>Gather
                      the documents you want to send and put them in the
                      order you want them to be received.</big></b></big></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><small><small><small><strike><big><big><b>Fill
                              out a separate piece of paper c</b>alled
                            a&nbsp;coversheet&nbsp;with the recipient's
                            name, fax number/phone number, your name,
                            your phone number, a short message </big><i>and
                            number of pages (including coversheet).</i></big></strike></small></small></small></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big><i>Lay
                    the doc</i><i><big>uments face-up in the fax machine
                      feeder tray with the coversheet on top</big></i></big></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big><i><big>Dial
                      the recipient's fax number<br>
                    </big></i></big></li>
              <li style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px;
                list-style-position: inside; word-wrap: break-word;"><big><big>Press
                    the&nbsp;"fax" or "send" button, depending on the
                    particular fax machine model</big></big></li>
            </ol>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
